text: Desmiphora chemsaki is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Giesbert in 1998. It is known from Mexico.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora chemsaki. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1998
